      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Instagram — Daily Collector\n\n**Schedule:** 06:00 UTC daily (08:00 Europe/Paris CEST)\n**Handles:** All Instagram handles with status=approved AND backfill data\n**Source:** Apify instagram-profile-scraper (~$0.003/profile)\n**Output:** channel_metrics + Master Sheet (one tab per handle)\n\n**Audit 2026-04-08:**\n- Switched empty schedule rule to explicit `0 6 * * *` (was never firing)\n- Added `status=eq.approved` filter on Fetch IG Handles\n- Normalized IF operator + Code node mode\n- Fixed mojibake em-dashes in jsCode\n",
        "height": 140,
        "width": 500,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "ig08-0001-4f7a-8b1c-000000000001",
      "name": "Daily IG Collector",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
